<paragraph id="2DE566ADFECFA17394150CE71709ADB6" pageId="0" pageNumber="41">Culture characters.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="75B82F883452D7E9BBD697D50BF4E857" pageId="0" pageNumber="41">Colony originally flat with white fluffy aerial mycelium, becoming greyish mycelium with age, with yellowish-cream conidial drops exuding from the ostioles.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
